<A>__{two squad cars parked in a v formation a makeshift roadblock. anxious policemen mill about in front of them. they move into position as the batmobile, still trailing smoke, rounds a corner and careens directly toward them... angle on batmobile that moment the front fender of the batmobile detaches and extends itself from the body of the car. it bends in the middle; wing panels flip into place, forming an arrowhead shaped cow catcher.}
